Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :EC STUDY - LESSONS LEARNT FROM EMERGENCIES AFTER
       ACCIDENTS     IN     DENMARK     INVOLVING    DANGEROUS    SUBSTANCES
Author                :GRONBERG C D
       SMITH-HANSEN L
       NIELSEN D S
Affiliation           :RISO NATIONAL LABORATORY, ROSKILDE (DK)
       RISO NATIONAL LABORATORY, ROSKILDE (DK)
       RISO NATIONAL LABORATORY, ROSKILDE (DK)
Bibliogr reference    :EUR 15562 EN (1994) 66 PP., FS, ECU 8.50 ISBN
       92-826-7515-7  OFFICE  FOR  OFFICIAL  PUBLICATIONS  OF  THE  EUROPEAN
       COMMUNITIES, L-2985 LUXEMBOURG
Abstract              :This report discusses Danish accidents involving
       dangerous  substances.  These  have been reviewed in order to analyse
       experience  with mitigation procedures and emergency organisation. It
       reports  on  the  status  and  principal  changes  underway in Danish
       emergency  organisations  which  may  be  significant with respect to
       chemical  emergencies. The lessons to be learnt are examined and data
       sheets for the cases investigated are presented.
