Abstract              :The report collects papers presented at the
       International   Conference   Technological   Innovations   in   Civil
       Protection held in Florence on 17 - 20 March l993, in the sessions on
       legislation  on  industrial  risk at a EEC level, and at national and
       regional level in Italy, methodologies for industrial risk assessment
