Title in english      :COMMUNITY DOCUMENTATION CENTRE ON INDUSTRIAL RISK :
       REVIEW      OF      ENVIRONMENTAL     ACCIDENTS     AND     INCIDENTS
Author                :LINDGAARD-JORGENSEN P
       BENDER K
Affiliation           :WATER QUALITY INSTITUTE - RESEARCH CENTRE, HORSHOLM
       (DK)
       WATER QUALITY INSTITUTE - RESEARCH CENTRE, HORSHOLM (DK)
Bibliogr reference    :EUR 14002 EN (1992) 86 PP., FS, ECU 7.50 ISBN
       92-826-3535-X  OFFICE  FOR  OFFICIAL  PUBLICATIONS  OF  THE  EUROPEAN
       COMMUNITIES, L-2985 LUXEMBOURG
Abstract              :The aim of this study was to gather information from
       literature or databases on accidents with environmental consequences,
       in  order to produce a clearer definition of environmental hazard, to
       be used with the Directive 82/501 and its fundamental revision.
       Accidents   from  transport,  storage  and  processing  of  hazardous
