<HEAD>
<TITLE>
REVIEW OF TRANSPORTATION ACCIDENTS OF HAZARDOUS
MATERIALS
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :199110751
Quality valid. date   :1994-12-02
Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :REVIEW OF TRANSPORTATION ACCIDENTS OF HAZARDOUS
       MATERIALS
Author                :HAASTRUP P
       BROCKHOFF L
Affiliation           :JRC ISPRA (IT)
       JRC ISPRA (IT)
Bibliogr reference    :PAPER PRESENTED: HAZARDOUS SUBSTANCES : SAFETY IN
       TRANSPORT,  KARLSRUHE  (DE), JUNE 10-12, 1991 AVAILABLE FROM EUROPEAN
       COMMISSION,   DGXIII/D-2,   L-2920  LUXEMBOURG  AS  PAPER  36178  ORA
Abstract              :Two studies on accidents relating to the
       transportation  of  hazardous materials are presented. The main focus
       of  the  analyses was given to accidents from rail, road and pipeline
       transportation  and  to  comparisons with the corresponding accidents
       from  fixed installations. 1793 accidents are classified according to
       accident  situation,  transportation mode and consequences. Frequency
       fatalities  curves  are  plotted.  The variability of the information
       found  in accident case reporting is analysed for 595 cases described
       more  than once in the literature. It is concluded that approximately
       one  third  of  the  accidents  involving  hazardous chemicals happen
       during  transportation.  No  difference is found between the relative
       severity   of   transportation   accidents  and  accidents  at  fixed
       installations.  The  quality  of the information provided by accident
       reporting  was found to be low. It is suggested that this is inherent
       to  the  reporting  process  and  subsequent selection of information
       thought to be important, rather than arising from unreliable sources.
       Uncertainty  is  therefore inherent in the data and in any subsequent
       analysis.
Facet codes           :314 Transportation
Availability in lang  :en English
Publication year      :1991
Publication type      :ORA An oral conference paper
Euroabstracts number  :EAB129128900
Subject index codes   :TRA (TRANSPORT)
 
            --------------------------------------------------
 
 
</PRE>
