A GENERAL METHOD FOR ASSESSING THE THERMAL STABILITY
OF BATCH CHEMICAL REACTORS
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :199411482
Quality valid. date   :1994-12-06
Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :A GENERAL METHOD FOR ASSESSING THE THERMAL STABILITY
       OF  BATCH  CHEMICAL  REACTORS  BY  SENSITIVITY  CALCULATIONS BASED ON
       LYAPUNOV EXPONENTS
Author                :STROZZI F
       ZALDIVAR J M
Affiliation           :JRC ISPRA (IT)
       JRC ISPRA (IT)
Bibliogr reference    :ARTICLE: CHEMICAL ENGINEERING SCIENCE, VOL. 49 (1994)
       NO. 16, PP. 2681-2688
Abstract              :A new method is presented for calculating the
       parametric   sensitivity,  or  thermal  runaway,  of  batch  chemical
       reactors.  In this work, sensitivity is calculated using the Lyapunov
       exponents.  The calculated criterion is compared with the generalised
       criterion for parametric sensitivity and with other data generated.
