<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :199310465
Quality valid. date   :1994-11-29
Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :THE AVAILABILITY OF OCCUPATIONAL EXPOSURE DATA IN THE
       EUROPEAN COMMUNITY
Author                :SMITH M H P
       GLASS D C
Affiliation           :UNIVERSITY OF BIRMINGHAM, INSTITUTE OF OCCUPATIONAL
       HEALTH (GB)
       UNIVERSITY OF BIRMINGHAM, INSTITUTE OF OCCUPATIONAL HEALTH (GB)
Bibliogr reference    :EUR 14378 EN (1993) 132 PP., FS, ECU 13.50 ISBN
       92-826-4331-X  OFFICE  FOR  OFFICIAL  PUBLICATIONS  OF  THE  EUROPEAN
       COMMUNITIES, L-2985 LUXEMBOURG
Abstract              :This report describes a study undertaken to identify
       sources  of occupational exposure data in the European Community. The
       need  for  access  to  occupational exposure data is reviewed and the
       form of the exposure data resources found in the study is described.
       Descriptions   of  the  41  computerised  databanks  of  occupational
       exposure data identified are also included.
