<HEAD>
<TITLE>
INFORMATION SERVICE ON CHEMICAL SUBSTANCES AND
PRODUCTS
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :199310440
Quality valid. date   :1994-11-29
Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :INFORMATION SERVICE ON CHEMICAL SUBSTANCES AND
       PRODUCTS
Note                  :EXPERIENCES FROM A TELEPHONE INFORMATION SERVICE
Author                :HANSEN L F
       FRIES A S
Affiliation           :DANISH NATIONAL INSTITUTE OF OCCUPATIONAL HEALTH,
       COPENHAGEN (DK)
       DANISH NATIONAL INSTITUTE OF OCCUPATIONAL HEALTH, COPENHAGEN (DK)
Bibliogr reference    :EUR 14177 EN (1993) 26 PP., FS, ECU 6 ISBN
       92-826-4293-3  OFFICE  FOR  OFFICIAL  PUBLICATIONS  OF  THE  EUROPEAN
       COMMUNITIES, L-2985 LUXEMBOURG
Abstract              :The report describes experiences with a public
       telephone  information service on chemical substances and products at
       the  Danish  National Institute of Occupational Health (DNIOH) with a
       view to establishing a similar telephone information service in other
       member  countries  of  the European Community. The report presents an
       analysis  of  calls,  users,  cases  and  topics,  and  describes the
       organisation  of  the  service,  and  the back-up documentation. As a
       result  of  the  introduction  of  this  service,  there  has  been a
       considerable decrease in the number of written enquiries; 71 % of the
       telephone  enquiries  are  answered  directly  during  the call, thus
       speeding  up  the  response time. It is suggested that monitoring the
       queries raised can produce useful feedback concerning those products,
       substances or processes which give rise to problems in the workplace.
Facet codes           :001 Documentation and information science
       538 Safety and health at work
Availability in lang  :en English
Publication year      :1993
Publication type      :EUR A report issued by the Commission as an EUR
       report      and      identified      by      its      EUR      number
Euroabstracts number  :EAB131103100
Subject index codes   :SAF (SAFETY)
       INF (INFORMATION, MEDIA)
 
            --------------------------------------------------
 
 
</PRE>
