<TITLE>
OCCUPATIONAL EXPOSURE LIMITS
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :199411578
Quality valid. date   :1995-03-21
Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :OCCUPATIONAL EXPOSURE LIMITS : CRITERIA DOCUMENT FOR
       1,1-DICHLOROETHANE
Author                :GARLANDA T
       BASILICO S
Affiliation           :EUROPEAN COMMISSION, LUXEMBOURG (LU)
       EUROPEAN COMMISSION, LUXEMBOURG (LU)
Bibliogr reference    :EUR 15960 EN (1995) 26 PP., FS, ECU 7 ISBN
       92-826-9117-9  OFFICE  FOR  OFFICIAL  PUBLICATIONS  OF  THE  EUROPEAN
       COMMUNITIES, L-2985 LUXEMBOURG
Abstract              :This publication contains a criteria document for the
       establishment   of  an  occupational  exposure  limit  value  for  1,
       1-dichloroethane.  The  objective of the study was to collect a broad
       spectrum of relevant data on 1,1-dichloroethane chemistry, production
        occurrence  in the workplace, toxicology, and evaluation of existing
       occupational  exposure  limits, where known. All data are interpreted
       with  respect to human health risk and occupational exposure, and are
       summarised  at  the end of the report. This criteria document will be
       used  in  the  preparation  of  legislation  on  limit values for the
       protection of workers from the risks related to exposure to chemical,
       physical and biological agents at work.
Facet codes           :538 Safety and health at work
Availability in lang  :en English
Publication year      :1995
Publication type      :EUR A report issued by the Commission as an EUR
       report      and      identified      by      its      EUR      number
Euroabstracts number  :EAB133151500
Subject index codes   :SAF (SAFETY)
 
            --------------------------------------------------
 
 
