Abstract              :This publication contains a criteria document for the
       establishment  of  an  occupational  exposure limit value for diethyl
       ether.  The objective of the study was to collect a broad spectrum of
       relevant  data  on diethyl ether chemistry, production, occurrence in
       the  workplace,  toxicology,  and evaluation of existing occupational
       exposure  limits,  where known. All data are interpreted with respect
       to human health risk and occupational exposure, and are summarised at
       the end of the report.
