       CONSTRUCTIONS
Author                :EUROFER
Affiliation           :STEEL PROMOTION COMMITTEE, BRUXELLES (BE)
Bibliogr reference    :EUR 12208 EN (1990) 83 PP., MF, ECU 4 OFFICE FOR
