<TITLE>
OCCUPATIONAL EXPOSURE LIMITS
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :199411580
Quality valid. date   :1995-03-21
Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :OCCUPATIONAL EXPOSURE LIMITS : CRITERIA DOCUMENT FOR
       N-HEXANE
Author                :GARLANDA T
       BASILICO S
Affiliation           :EUROPEAN COMMISSION, LUXEMBOURG (LU)
       EUROPEAN COMMISSION, LUXEMBOURG (LU)
Bibliogr reference    :EUR 15962 EN (1995) 102 PP., FS, ECU 11.50 ISBN
       92-826-9132-2  OFFICE  FOR  OFFICIAL  PUBLICATIONS  OF  THE  EUROPEAN
       COMMUNITIES, L-2985 LUXEMBOURG
Abstract              :This publication contains a criteria document for the
       establishment of an occupational exposure limit value for n-hexane.
       The  objective  of  the  study  was  to  collect  a broad spectrum of
       relevant  data  on  n-hexane chemistry, production, occurrence in the
       workplace,   toxicology,  and  evaluation  of  existing  occupational
       exposure  limits,  where known. All data are interpreted with respect
       to human health risk and occupational exposure, and are summarised at
       the  end  of  the  report. This criteria document will be used in the
       preparation  of  legislation  on  limit  values for the protection of
       workers  from the risks related to exposure to chemical, physical and
       biological agents at work.
