Record cntrl number   :199410242
Quality valid. date   :1994-11-28
Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :TWO-PHASE RELEASES OF TOXIC AND FLAMMABLE
       SUBSTANCES/THERMAL   INITIATION,   SOURCE   TERM   AND  FIRE  EFFECTS
Note                  :FINAL REPORT
Author                :BARTON J A
       MOODIE K
Affiliation           :HEALTH AND SAFETY EXECUTIVE, EXPLOSION AND FLAME
       LABORATORY, BUXTON (GB)
       HEALTH AND SAFETY EXECUTIVE, EXPLOSION AND FLAME LABORATORY, BUXTON
       (GB)
