<HEAD>
<TITLE>
MEASUREMENT STATION FOR TRANSDUCERS WITH INTEGRATED PROCESSING
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :199210560
Quality valid. date   :1994-12-02
Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :MEASUREMENT STATION FOR TRANSDUCERS WITH INTEGRATED
       PROCESSING - PART 2
Original title        :MESS-STATION FR MESSWERTGEBER MIT INTEGRIERTER
       VERARBEITUNG - TEIL 2
Note                  :ABSCHLUBERICHT
Author                :DMT GESELLSCHAFT FR FORSCHUNG UND PRFUNG GMBH
Affiliation           :DMT GESELLSCHAFT FR FORSCHUNG UND PRFUNG MBH,
       BOCHUM (DE)
Bibliogr reference    :EUR 13980 DE (1992) 58 PP., MF, ECU 4, BLOW-UP COPY
       ECU  9  OFFICE FOR OFFICIAL PUBLICATIONS OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES,
       L-2985 LUXEMBOURG
Abstract              :In the course of four research and development
       projects,  transducers  for  the  central  monitoring  of underground
       operations  were  developed and tested along with the associated data
       collection   and   transmission  equipment.  Close  cooperation  with
       companies   and   improvement   of   the  electrical  and  mechanical
       construction  during  equipment  testing were the main aspects of the
       work.   At  the  same  time,  technical  support  was  given  in  the
       establishment  and  introduction of analog and digital interfaces for
       German  hard  coal  mining.  A measurement system was thus developed,
       with  sensors  to monitor: - pressures in gaseous and liquid media; -
       mechanical   stresses;  -  angles  of  rotation;  -  temperatures  in
       different  media  and  at parts of machines; - electrical values. The
       measurement   system  comprises  data  collection  equipment,  either
       connected  in  series  via  a  bus system to wider remote control and
       transmission  systems,  or  capable  of  operating  independently. As
       regards its explosion proof characteristics, its essential components
       rate  as  inherently  safe, and the system has thus been approved for
       use underground.
Facet codes           :410 Coal research, general and miscellaneous
Availability in lang  :de German
Publication year      :1992
Publication type      :EUR A report issued by the Commission as an EUR
       report      and      identified      by      its      EUR      number
