<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :199410857
Quality valid. date   :1994-11-28
Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :FORMENTOR : REAL-TIME OPERATOR ADVISORY SYSTEM FOR
       LOSS    CONTROL    :    APPLICATION   TO   A   PETRO-CHEMICAL   PLANT
Author                :WILIKENS M
       BURTON C J
Affiliation           :JRC ISPRA (IT)
       HOSKYNS GROUP PLC, LONDON (GB)
Bibliogr reference    :PAPER PRESENTED: COMPUTER AIDED ERGONOMICS & SAFETY
       (12TH  CONGRESS),  TORONTO  (CA),  AUGUST  15-19, 1994 AVAILABLE FROM
       EUROPEAN  COMMISSION, DGXIII/D-2, L-2920 LUXEMBOURG AS PAPER EN 38373
       ORA
Abstract              :This paper describes one of the developed FORMENTOR
       pilot  applications,  a  supervisory  and decision support system for
       operators  of  an  extractive  distillation  unit of a petro-chemical
       plant. The most important techniques and models used are discussed.
       The  developed  FORMENTOR  system  has  been  installed  on  the unit
       operated  by  BP-Chemicals  Ltd. and its performance in responding to
       real plant upsets has been evaluated.
