<TITLE>
TOWARDS THE PREDICTION OF VENTING CHARACTERISTICS
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :198910378
Quality valid. date   :1994-12-01
Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :TOWARDS THE PREDICTION OF VENTING CHARACTERISTICS
       WITH THE CODES SAFIRE AND DEERS
Author                :SKOULOUDIS A N
       KOTTOWSKI H M
       BELL K I
       OSTER R
Affiliation           :JRC ISPRA ESTAB. (IT)
       JRC ISPRA ESTAB. (IT)
       JRC ISPRA ESTAB. (IT)
       JRC ISPRA ESTAB. (IT)
Bibliogr reference    :PAPER PRESENTED: INTERNATIONAL SYMPOSIUM ON RUNAWAY
       REACTIONS,  CAMBRIDGE,  MASSACHUSETTS (US), MARCH 7-9, 1989 AVAILABLE
       FROM  EUROPEAN  COMMISSION, DGXIII/D-2, L-2920 LUXEMBOURG AS PAPER EN
       34625 ORA
Abstract              :Depressurisation phenomena of different containers
       are  analysed  by  the  computer  codes  SAFIRE  and  DEERS.  Several
       comparisons between experiments and calculations with the codes under
       consideration  here,  are made. The parameters treated in the present
       work are the pressure and mass inventory of the vessel. The following
       were  examined:  the  influence  of  flow  regimes in the vessel, the
       influence  of  the sizing parameters for the vessel, the influence of
       the starting conditions, and the dependence on the type of the vent.
Facet codes           :818 Reactor safety
