<TITLE>
DATA, MODELS, ESTIMATION METHODS AND PROBLEMS RELATING TO RELIABILITY DATA BOOKS
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :199510961
Quality valid. date   :1995-08-10
Update date           :1996-01-19
Title in english      :DATA, MODELS, ESTIMATION METHODS AND PROBLEMS
       RELATING TO RELIABILITY DATA BOOKS
Author                :ARSENIS S
Affiliation           :JRC ISPRA (IT)
Bibliogr reference    :ARTICLE: EUROPEAN INDUSTRY RELIABILITY DATA BANK
Abstract              :The objective of this methodological appendix is to
       summarise  and review estimation procedures developed and implemented
       for  the  estimation  of  failure rates of components for reliability
       data  books. All the procedures cited have been derived under various
       mathematical models. The paper discusses the postulates common in the
       models and highlights their differences.
