       XIII/A2,     BP     1907,    MENTIONING    PAPER    ORA    34207    E
Abstract              :THE EXPERIMENTAL FACILITY FIRES AT THE JRC-ISPRA HAS
       BEEN  DESIGNED  TO  PROVIDE  DATA  ON  CHEMICAL  REACTIONS UNDERGOING
       RUNAWAY  CONDITIONS.  IN THIS REPORT THE MAIN SAFETY CRITERIA APPLIED
       TO  THE  PLANT  AS  DISCUSSED.  IN  PARTICULAR  THE  RESPONSE  OF THE
