<TITLE>
RUNAWAY REACTIONS
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :199311064
Quality valid. date   :1994-11-29
Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :RUNAWAY REACTIONS : PREVENTION AND PROTECTION
       MEASURES
Original title        :LE REAZIONI 'RUNAWAY' : MISURE DI PREVENZIONE E
       PROTEZIONE
Author                :BENUZZI A
Affiliation           :JRC ISPRA (IT)
Bibliogr reference    :ARTICLE: PREVENZIONE, VOL. 18 (1993) PP. 7-10
Abstract              :Frequent and often serious chemical accidents are due
       to  runaway  reactions.  The basic phenomenology and the prime causes
       which  lead  to  runaways,  as  well  as the prevention measures that
       should  be  adopted,  are  reviewed  in this report. In addition, the
       plant  protection  and the accident mitigation methods, which must be
       enforced  in case of occurrence of a runaway, are discussed. Finally,
       an assessment strategy for chemical reaction hazards is outlined.
