       report      and      identified      by      its      EUR      number
Euroabstracts number  :EAB12914900
Programme acronym     :JRC-RELISTRU C
Reference to project  :JRC-RELISTRU C
Commission service    :JRC
Subject index codes   :SAF (SAFETY)
 
