<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :199410733
Quality valid. date   :1994-12-06
Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :SAFETY MANAGEMENT SYSTEMS IN THE PROCESS INDUSTRY
Note                  :PROCEEDINGS : CEC SEMINAR ON 7/8 OCTOBER, 1993 :
       RAVELLO (SA), ITALY
Author                :CACCIABUE P C
       GERBAULET I
       MITCHISON N (EDITORS)
Affiliation           :JRC ISPRA (IT)
       JRC ISPRA (IT)
       JRC ISPRA (IT)
Bibliogr reference    :EUR 15743 EN (1994) 214 PP., FS, ECU 21.50 ISBN
       92-826-8223-4  OFFICE  FOR  OFFICIAL  PUBLICATIONS  OF  THE  EUROPEAN
       COMMUNITIES, L-2985 LUXEMBOURG
Abstract              :Experts on safety management systems (SMS), both from
       the  national  authorities  and  from  industry,  participated in the
       seminar,  which  was divided into three sessions: (i) key elements of
       SMS  with  respect to the Seveso Directive; (ii) practical experience
       with SMS; (iii) performance measurements of SMS. For each session, in
       addition  to  the  papers  presented,  this  publication  includes  a
       rapporteur's report, comprising introductory remarks and a summary of
       the  session.  Also included is the report of the rapporteur from the
       final round table discussion.
