<TITLE>
MAJOR HAZARDS REGULATION IN THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITY
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :199110442
Quality valid. date   :1994-12-02
Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :MAJOR HAZARDS REGULATION IN THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITY
Author                :AMENDOLA A
Affiliation           :JRC ISPRA (IT)
Bibliogr reference    :PAPER PRESENTED: PROBABILISTIC SAFETY ASSESSMENT AND
       MANAGEMENT  (PSAM),  BEVERLEY  HILLS, CALIFORNIA (US), FEB. 4-7, 1991
       AVAILABLE  FROM EUROPEAN COMMISSION, DGXIII/D-2, L-2920 LUXEMBOURG AS
       PAPER EN 35692 ORA
Abstract              :The paper summarises the content of the EEC Directive
       on the control of major accident hazards of industrial activities and
       gives some insight into national requirements for the safety report.
       It  discusses  briefly some open problems such as risk communication,
       land-use   planning,   control   of   transport   accident   hazards,
       environmental   risk   and   the   recently   adopted  directives  on
       biotechnology hazards.
Facet codes           :312 Safety engineering
Availability in lang  :en English
Publication year      :1991
Publication type      :ORA An oral conference paper
Euroabstracts number  :EAB12993000
Subject index codes   :SAF (SAFETY)
 
            --------------------------------------------------
 
 
