<TITLE>
EARTHQUAKE HAZARD ASSESSMENT
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :199111139
Quality valid. date   :1994-12-02
Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :EARTHQUAKE HAZARD ASSESSMENT
Note                  :PROCEEDINGS OF THE EUROPEAN SCHOOL OF CLIMATOLOGY AND
       NATURAL  HAZARDS  COURSE,  HELD  IN  ATHENS  FROM  9  TO  16 MAY 1988
Author                :FANTECHI R
       ALMEIDA-TEIXEIRA M E (EDITORS)
Affiliation           :CEC BRUXELLES (BE)
       CEC BRUXELLES (BE)
Bibliogr reference    :EUR 13408 EN (1991) 195 PP., FS, ECU 16.25 ISBN
       92-826-2778-0  OFFICE  FOR  OFFICIAL  PUBLICATIONS  OF  THE  EUROPEAN
       COMMUNITIES, L-2985 LUXEMBOURG
Abstract              :As part of the training and education activities of
       EPOCH,  courses  are  held  in cooperation with European institutions
       involving  the  execution  of Community RTD programmes on climatology
       and  natural  hazards.  The present volume gives the text of lectures
       delivered  at  the  course held in May 1988 in Athens (Greece) on the
       subject of "Earthquake hazard assessment". Topics covered include the
       geodynamics  of  the  Mediterranean  domain, the design of earthquake
       resistant  structures,  aspects  of seismography, modelling of strong
       ground motion, and prediction techniques.
