<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :199310842
Quality valid. date   :1994-11-29
Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :OCCUPATIONAL EXPOSURE LIMITS : CRITERIA DOCUMENT FOR
       TOLUENE
Author                :JELNES J E
Affiliation           :DANISH NATIONAL INSTITUTE OF OCCUPATIONAL HEALTH,
       DEPARTMENT    OF    TOXICOLOGY    AND    BIOLOGY,   COPENHAGEN   (DK)
Bibliogr reference    :EUR 14212 EN (1993) 71 PP., FS, ECU 9 ISBN
       92-826-4284-4  OFFICE  FOR  OFFICIAL  PUBLICATIONS  OF  THE  EUROPEAN
       COMMUNITIES, L-2985 LUXEMBOURG
Abstract              :This criteria document establishes an occupational
       exposure  limit  value for toluene. The objective of the study was to
       collect  a  broad  spectrum  of  relevant  data on toluene chemistry,
       production,  occurrence  in the workplace, toxicology, and evaluation
       of  existing  occupational exposure limits, where known. All data are
       interpreted  with  respect  to  human  health  risk  and occupational
       exposure, and are summarised at the end of the report.
