Title in english      :THE TOXICOLOGY OF CHEMICALS 1. CARCINOGENICITY -
       VOLUME II
Note                  :SUMMARY REVIEWS OF THE SCIENTIFIC EVIDENCE
Author                :BERLIN A
       DRAPER M
       KRUG E
       ROI R
       VAN DER VENNE M T
Affiliation           :CEC LUXEMBOURG (LU)
       CEC LUXEMBOURG (LU)
