       92-825-9790-3  OFFICE  FOR  OFFICIAL  PUBLICATIONS  OF  THE  EUROPEAN
       COMMUNITIES, L-2985 LUXEMBOURG
Abstract              :This book provides summary reviews of the salient
       scientific evidence relevant to the assessment of the carcinogenicity
       of  21  particular  chemical compounds including nickel compounds. It
       also  gives  a  general  introduction to the chemistry and biology of
       nickel and its industrial and health prospects.
