<TITLE>
CHOKE PRESSURE IN PIPELINE RESTRICTIONS
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :199511504
Quality valid. date   :1995-11-03
Update date           :1996-01-19
Title in english      :CHOKE PRESSURE IN PIPELINE RESTRICTIONS
Author                :MORRIS S D
Affiliation           :JRC ISPRA (IT)
Bibliogr reference    :ARTICLE: JOURNAL OF HAZARDOUS MATERIALS (1995)
Abstract              :A simple analytical formula is derived for the choke
       pressure in a pipeline restriction discharging gas. This differs from
       the  standard  formula based on ideal nozzle flow in that lower choke
       pressures  are  predicted.  The  formula  may  be applied directly to
       safety valves.
