<TITLE>
TOP-VENTING OF FLASHING HIGH-VISCOSITY FLUIDS
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number   :199310140
Quality valid. date   :1994-11-29
Update date           :1996-01-20
Title in english      :TOP-VENTING OF FLASHING HIGH-VISCOSITY FLUIDS
Author                :MORRIS S D
       BELL K
       OSTER R
Affiliation           :JRC ISPRA (IT)
       JRC ISPRA (IT)
       JRC ISPRA (IT)
Bibliogr reference    :ARTICLE: CHEMICAL ENGINEERING AND PROCESSING, VOL. 31
       (1992), PP. 297-305
Abstract              :Experimental data are presented for top-venting of
       flashing  high-viscosity fluids. In addition, a practical vent-sizing
       method  is described which is applicable to such problems. The method
       employs  a  viscosity  factor which is correlated to the experimental
       data  for  fluids  with  viscosities  ranging up to 750 cP at initial
       conditions.  Although  principally  aimed  at venting of non-reacting
       vapour pressure systems, this work is of interest also for chemically
       reacting systems.
