<HEAD>
<TITLE>
BENCHMARK EXERCICE ON MAJOR HAZARD ANALYSIS
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number    :11990
Quality valid. date    :1994-01-23
Update date            :1995-08-12
Title                  :BENCHMARK EXERCICE ON MAJOR HAZARD ANALYSIS
Subject index codes    :SAF (SAFETY)
Other indexes          :EFFECTS OF TECHNOLOGY
                        RISK EVALUATION
                        DATA PROCESSING
                        COMPUTER PROGRAMMES
Objectives             :DEFINITION OF HAZARDOUS EVENT.
General information    :THIS PROJECT IS A CONTRIBUTION TO THE BRENCHMARK
EXERCICE,  TO  BE  CARRIED  OUT  ON  A  SINGLE  SUBJECT  INSTALLATION
COMPRISING :
-  A  SEA  TERMINAL  (IMPORTANT OF REFRIGERATED AMMONIA TO A 15000 TE
STORAGE TANK)
- PIPELINE TO THE PROCESS PLANT
- IN-PLANT PRESSURISED STORAGE METHOD
TECHNICA  WILL  USE ITS COMPREHENSIVE RISK ANALYSIS COMPUTER PACKAGE,
SAFETI, TO ANALYSE THIS INSTALLATION, USING TWO MODES OF ANALYSIS:
(I) FAST ANALYSIS, USING ALL THE DEFAULT OPTION AND OTHER FEATURES OF
SAFETI WHICH ALLOW RAPID PRODUCTION OF RISK CONTOURS (ALSO F-N CURVES
WHICH HOWEVER ARE OUTSIDE THE SCOPE OF THE BENCHMARK EXERCICE).
(II)  DETAILED  ANALYSIS, IN WHICH MORE MANUAL EFFORT IS PUT INTO THE
PREPARATION  OF DATA FOR SAFETI, DEFAULT OPTIONS ARE NOT USED SO MUCH
AND ANY SPECIAL HAZARDS GET MORE THOROUGH TREATMENT.
IN  ADDITION,  THE  DUTCH MINISTERY OF HOUSING, PHYSICAL PLANNING AND
ENVIRONMENT  WILL  BE  DOING  AN  INDEPENDENT RUN OF SAFETI USING THE
"FAST"  MODE  (I)  ABOVE.  THIS  WILL MAKE IT POSSIBLE TO EXAMINE THE
VARIATION BETWEEN TEAMS (USING THE SAME METHODOLOGY) AND ALSO BETWEEN
METHODOLOGIES (FAST OR DETAILED) USING THE SAME TEAM.
OUTLINED BELOW ARE STEPS IN RISK ASSESSMENT AS EMBODIED IN THE SAFETI
PACKAGE.
1. DATA COLLECTION
2. DEFINITION OF HAZARDOUS EVENTS
3. FREQUENCY ESTIMATES
4. SEISMIC ANALYSIS
5. CONSEQUENCE ANALYSIS
6. RISK IMPACT ANALYSIS
7. REANALYSIS
Start date             :1987-10-01
End date               :1989-08-31
Duration in months     :23
Project status         :Completed
Programme acronym      :TECHHAZ C
Subprogramme area      :HUMAN FACTOR  MAN-MACHINE INTERACTION (86-90)
Project reference      :EV4T0024
Prime contr org        :Technica Ltd
Prime contr address    :7-12 Tavistock Square
Prime contr postcode   :WC1H 9LT
Prime contr town       :London
Prime contr region     :R755 GREATER LONDON
Prime contr country    :GB (UNITED KINGDOM)
Contact person         :Name:         COX R.A.
                    Tel:          +44-1-382684
 
            --------------------------------------------------
</PRE>
