<TITLE>
BENCHMARK EXERCISE ON MAJOR HAZARD ANALYSIS
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number    :11989
Quality valid. date    :1994-01-23
Update date            :1995-08-12
Title                  :BENCHMARK EXERCISE ON MAJOR HAZARD ANALYSIS
Subject index codes    :SAF (SAFETY)
