Update date            :1995-08-12
Title                  :Development of sensors for CO, total products of
       combustion, NO2,  NOx,  CH4  and  total  flammable  gases  in  mine
       atmospheres using solid-state sensors combined with  microprocessor
       techniques
Subject index codes    :SAF (SAFETY)

