<HTML>
<HEAD>
<TITLE>
FLADIS field test analysis
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number    :27100 
Quality valid. date    :1995-06-14
Update date            :1995-08-12
Title                  :FLADIS field test analysis
Subject index codes    :ENV (ENVIRONMENTAL PROTECTION)
                        MET (METEOROLOGY)
                        SAF (SAFETY)
General information    :Parallel to the FLADIS PROJECT (Research on the
dispersion  of  two-phase release) field experiments are
carried out by a separate contract ("FLADIS field tests", coordinated
by  RISO National Laboratory). The results of field tests will become
available  by  the  end  of  1993  and beginning of 1994. In order to
enable  to  analyse the data within the main FLADIS PROJECT (original
final  date 31-3-1994) an extension of 6 month is Proposed, with main
aim to enable the university partners to extent their contribution.
Moreover  some  additional efforts are anticipated, which appear from
the current FLADIS project to be of importance:
-  extended statistical analysis of concentration fluctuation data; -
validation of a code for gas jets against field data;
-  assessment  of equivalent source term concepts to be used for wind
tunnel simulations against field data;
- application of CFD calculations on actual field test conditions.
The  results of this extension will be included in the reports of the
main FLADIS project.
