<HEAD>
<TITLE>
Comparison of flamelet and PDF models with detailed
experimental data for premixed turbulent cumbustion 
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Key words              :Explosion, flame propagation, turbulent combustion, 
                        modelling
Record cntrl number    :26278
Quality valid. date    :1995-03-23
Update date            :1995-08-12
Title                  :Comparison of flamelet and PDF models with detailed
                        experimental data for premixed turbulent cumbustion
Subject index codes    :COO (COORDINATION, COOPERATION) SCI (SCIENTIFIC 
                        RESEARCH)

The objective of this study is to provide accurate experimental 
measurements of the flame propagation in premixed gaseous charge under 
different intensity and scale of turbulence. Research will be carried out 
in cylindrical chambers and different grids will be used to generate 
initial turbulence in the mixture. Part of research will be carried out in 
a single compression machine, where turbulence will be generated by a rapid 
movement of piston. Compressed gaseous mixture will pass through different 
turbulence generated grids, so prior to ignition, turbulence of different 
scale and intensity will be generated. Turbulence intensity and scale 
depend not only on size of the introduced grid, but alson on initial 
pressure and the speed of compression. Turbulence intensity and scale will 
be measured by a hot anemometry. Flame propagation will be measured by a 
high speed direct photography and the effectiveness of combustion will be 
estimated on the basis of pressure measurements.This research will be 
estimated on the basis of pressure measurements. This research will be 
carried out for a gaseous mixtures of different composition and initial 
pressure.

Start date             :1994-05-01
End date               :1995-04-30
Duration in months     :12
Project status         :Completed
Programme acronym      :ICPECO C
Project reference      :CIPD930302
Prime contr org        :Rheinisch-Westfaelische Technische Hochschule 
                        Aachen
Prime Organization Type:EDU Education
