<HEAD>
<TITLE>
Simple model for calculating the fire resistance of composite floors and beams
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number    :6944
Quality valid. date    :1994-01-24
Key words              :Steel buildings, fire resistance
Update date            :1995-08-28
Title                  :Simple model for calculating the fire resistance of
                        composite floors and beams
Subject index codes    :IND (INDUSTRIAL MANUFACTURE)
                        MAT (MATERIALS TECHNOLOGY)

Objectives             :This second phase of previously supported research
(ECSC  contract  nr  7210-SA/509)  will develop a simple mathematical
model to calculate the resistance of floors and mixed beams to fire.
The  mathematical  model  for  steel  sections developed in the first
phase of the work will now be extended to steel-concrete sections.
The  research  will  be  carried  out  jointly  by  ARBED  Recherches
(Luxembourg), TNO, Delft (The Netherlands), INSA, Rennes (France) and
CTICM,   Paris   (France)   with   the  latter  acting  as  technical
co-ordinator.

