<TITLE>
Brochure on fire safety of steel structures
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number    :14221
Quality valid. date    :1990-10-22
Key words              :Steel buildings, guidelines, fire safety concept
Update date            :1995-08-28
Title                  :Brochure on fire safety of steel structures
Subject index codes    :IND (INDUSTRIAL  MANUFACTURE)MAT (MATERIALS 
                        TECHNOLOGY)

Objectives             :Architects, no-professional decision makers and
investors  need guidelines covering the major aspects of fire safety,
especially   for   steel   constructions,  which  are  explained  and
accessible.  For  this  audience, available literature is not easy to
understand  and  does  not  provide a rapid overview. This project is
intended  to  study  and draw up the text for a succint brochure with
the  aim  of  presenting a large amount of information based on major
concepts, in combination with suitable illustrations, which will only
examine  theoretical  aspects  in  general terms in order to provid a
rapid, lively and convincing summary

