<TITLE>
Validation and optimization of an integrate information system for 
industrial risk management at the regional / subregional level
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<PRE>
Record cntrl number    :23987
Quality valid. date    :1995-02-22
Update date            :1995-08-28
Title                  :Validation and optimization of an integrate
                        information  system  for industrial risk management
                        at the regional / subregional level
Subject index codes    :ENV (ENVIRONMENTAL PROTECTION)
                        MET (METEOROLOGY)
                        SAF (SAFETY)
General information    :Taking into consideration the scientific and
technical  contents  and  partial  results of the preceeding proposal
(Research  Contract  No.  EV5V-CT92-0095,  under  realization),  this
additional  project  aims  to  achieve  the  optimization of the risk
