<DOCNO>WT26-B25-671</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA060-000333-B032-127</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.sustainable.doe.gov:80/barriers.html 205.168.79.33 19970115062459 text/html 9048
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 06:25:02 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5
