<DOCHDR>
http://www.sustainable.doe.gov:80/pubs/smartplaces.html 205.168.79.33 19970115062810 text/html 19683
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 06:28:15 GMT
