<U>To obtain report or for more information:</u>
<P>

Elizabeth Kline<BR>
Global Development and Environment Institute<BR>
Tufts University<BR>
Curtis Hall<BR>
474 Boston Avenue<BR>
Medford, MA  02155<BR>
(617)  628-5000, ext. 2075
