<BR><BR><BR>

<B><U>Guide to Sustainable Community Indicators</U></B> -- Maureen Hart
<P>A comprehensive examination of indicators and their role in the development of sustainable communities. Provides a list of sample indicators as well as a discussion on the characteristics of effective indicators.
